title: Mr.Time : Transkeleton

descriptionHTML:
*This watch face is only available for Android Wear. Tizen OS(Gear S2, S3) Users can download from Galaxy apps.

This watch is called 'Transkeleton'

[Mr.Time Watchface Series]
We provide various analog&digital watches with features and sub-dials.
More different designs will be updated constantly.

* Double tap : Skeleton Mode
comments: Love the moving bits This does actually work, despite what the other reviews are saying. The moving parts are smooth, and I had no problem downloading it.
